{
  "texts": [
    "In the subsample with high education levels, the issuance of green bonds has a more pronounced impact on ER.",
    "This finding uncovers a manager's positive role in promoting ER through green bond issuance, showing that enterprises with strong executive ability can better identify policy changes and the external environment.",
    "When enterprises issue green bonds, they will better identify their legitimacy requirements in the face of more stakeholders' participation; thus, managers' ability to handle and analyze problems can boost ER engagements.",
    "As shown in the institutional background in Sect.",
    "\"Institutional background for green bonds in China\" above, China's green bonds have prominent characteristics of industry bias."
  ]
}